Do you want to use Auto-Flash?

What is Auto-Flash Function ?

1.Automatically push update.zip to your device.
2.Automatically reboot into Fastboot mode and flash kernel.
3.Automatically Wipe Data and Cache(Your choice).
4.Automatically reboot into CWM-recovery Mode.

(The kernel I provided here are BlendMIUI kernel without overclock,if you want to flash other kernels you can put the kernel you like into BlendMIUI-kernel folder and replace the boot.img by yours but make sure to rename it as boot.img and put it into the right place!)
If you want to use Auto-Flash please enter "yes" to confirm.
If not,please enter "no" to continue.

